  "texts": [
    "This approach would not only enhance their understanding of ethical principles but also prepare them for decision-making in complex, real-life medical situations influenced by AI.",
    "It is important for future physicians to understand the balance between the potential benefits of AI and the ethical implications of its use, particularly in scenarios in which biased algorithms could lead to unequal treatment of diverse patient groups.",
    "Therefore, a comprehensive curriculum that includes both theoretical knowledge and practical applications is essential to cultivate ethically informed medical professionals.An in-depth and interdisciplinary understanding of ethics is important in the dynamic field of medical AI.",
    "This importance is underscored by the fact that the integration of AI into medical education may not always keep pace with rapid advancements in medical practice.",
    "A focus on ethical principles rather than solely on specific challenges of AI use in medicine aims to prepare medical students for various scenarios in the medical context."
  ],
